oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph identification of Cpl. Robert Brownlow Wilson
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photograph identification of Cpl. Robert Brownlow Wilson indicates his height of approximately 6' tall. The 575 is possibly part of his serial number. He served in Co. B, 117th Inf. Regt. during World War I. After the war, Cpl. Wilson returned to his life as a farmer in Blount County and lived to age 95.
